parameters.name: レクイエム・暗い場面

parameters:
\n<Ameria>"I'm sorry... It's all because I... because I overstepped,
that this..."
\n<Luerre>"I don't understand why you're apologizing to me."

\n<Luerre>"You did well. The fault lies with me... I'm sorry. It seems
I've caused you trouble because of my actions."

\n<Ameria>"It's because I failed! If I had been more careful, this
wouldn't have happened--!"

\n<Valam soldier>"Dispatched medical officer of Luerre, Luerre Theresa.
You've been informed already, haven't you?"

\n<Valam soldier>"This incident... it was your judgment, and even more so,
you gave treatment instructions to an apprentice medic....
Am I wrong?"

\n<Valam soldier>"Your actions have become a major issue in the imperial
homeland. The matter of right and wrong will be settled by
the homeland's judiciary, so for now, you will follow us."

\n<Luerre>"I'm sorry. Feel free to use this place as you like. All the
books, I'll give them all to you."

\n<Ameria>"I don't want that... I don't want to be separated from
Priest-sama! I want to learn so much more from you, and
besides, there's still--!"

\n<Ameria>"I still haven't properly thanked you for helping me! I hate
the idea of parting like this! Next time, I will be the one!
I will be the one to help Priest-sama...!"
Luerre placed her hand on Ameria's head.

\n<Luerre>"...Ameria. You are already a fine medical officer. Having a
good disciple like you makes me happy."
\n<Luerre>"But you haven't forgotten what I told you, have you?"

\n<Luerre>"You are kind and strong. But precisely because of that, you
must work harder than anyone else and learn correctly. Keep
practicing and slowly accumulate knowledge and skills."

\n<Luerre>"Now, now. Perhaps we did fail a bit this time.... What did
I tell you to do in such situations?"

\n<Ameria>"*hic*... *hic*... To challenge... and if I fail, to
reflect... to write it down in my journal..."

\n<Luerre>"That's right.... But there's one more thing you're
forgetting."

\n<Luerre>"Pray to God. Surely God will answer you who are working so
hard."
\n<Ameria>"What should I do... It's all my fault... It's all... me..."

\n<Ameria>"That's right... the journal... If I fail, I should write it
down in the journal and reflect..."
Ameria began to write in her journal.
Ameria threw away the journal she was writing in.

\n<Ameria>"Uuuuuaaaaaahhhhh!! What should I do! It's all my fault!
It's all because of meee!!"

\n<Ameria>"I'm sorry Priest-sama! It's all because of me! Because
someone like me overstepped!"
\n<Ameria>"Aaaaaahhhhh! I'm sorry! Everyone! I'm so sorryyyyy!!"

\n<Lyric>"Just when someone finally shows up, it's the crybaby
sister. Seriously... I can't get out because of the barrier
magic, and I thought I was going to starve to death here."

\n<Lyric>"Did you bring me here? I thought I was dead, but it turns
out I'm surprisingly alive. Anyway, let's start by you
telling me what's going on around here."
\n<Lyric>"Huh? Hey, wait a minute. I didn't do anything--"

\n<Ameria>"The-the-the corpse! The corpse is moving! A zombie!? A
ghost!!?"
\n<Lyric>"Ha... Hah!? A ghost!? No way, I'm alive!"

\n<Ameria>"I'm talking to a ghost!!! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
I apologize for leaving you behind, please don't be angry!"

\n<Lyric>"Wait--hold on, don't rush! Listen to me! I'm not a ghost,
and I won't do anything!"

\n<Ameria>"Evil spirits begone! Evil spirits begone! Evil spirits
begone!!"

\n<Lyric>"Wait wait wait wait wait wait!! I'm going to die! I'll
die!!"

am..."

\n<Ameria>"That's right... the diary... If I fail, I have to write it
in the diary, to reflect on it..."
Ameria began to write in her diary.

However, Ameria threw the diary she was writing onto the
floor midway.

\n<Ameria>"Uuuuuaaaaaahhh! What should I do! It's all my fault! It's
all because of meee!"

\n<Ameria>"Priest-sama! I'm sorry! It's all because of me! Because
someone like meee! Meddled too much!"
\n<Ameria>"Aaaaaaaaahhh! No, I don't want this! I hate being alone!!"

\n<Lyric>"I thought someone finally came, but it's just a tiny
crybaby Sister."

\n<Lyric>"Are you the one who brought me here? Trapped inside a
barrier in a church of all places. What on earth were you
thinking?"

\n<Lyric>"I thought I was dead, but surprisingly, I survived. Anyway,
let's start by you telling me everything about what happened
here."
\n<Lyric>"Hey, wait a minute. I didn't do anything--"
\n<Ameria>"A corpse! The corpse is moving! A ghost!? "
\n<Lyric>"Huh? Corpse? Ghost? No way, I'm alive!"

\n<Ameria>"I'm talking to a ghost!! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry! I
apologize for leaving you behind, please forgive me!"

\n<Lyric>"Wait...!? Hold on, don't rush! Listen to me! I'm not a
ghost, and I won't do anything!"

\n<Ameria>"Evil spirits begone! Evil spirits begone! Evil spirits
begone!!"

\n<Lyric>"Wait wait wait wait wait wait!! Seriously stop it! I'll
die! I'll really die!!"
